      "rendered": "[New Data] The 2023 Nonprofit Tech for Good Report"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "<p>The biennial <a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Nonprofit-Tech-for-Good-Report-Final2-2023.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Nonprofit Tech for Good Report</a> seeks to gain a better understanding of how nonprofit organizations use technology for digital marketing and fundraising. The 2023 report is based on the survey responses of 1,732 nonprofit professionals that subscribe to or follow Nonprofit Tech for Good on social media.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">Survey questions covered website and email communications, online fundraising, social media, and professional development in the nonprofit sector. The survey was promoted online in 2021 and 2022 and completed by nonprofit professionals from 116 countries.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"maxbutton-2 maxbutton maxbutton-download-now\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Download Now!\" rel=\"noopener\" href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/Nonprofit-Tech-for-Good-Report-Final2-2023.pdf\"><span class='mb-text'>Download Now!</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Email address not required!</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p>Our<strong>\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Certificate in Digital Marketing &amp; Fundraising</a>\u00a0program covers the fundamentals of website design, email marketing, online fundraising, and social media for nonprofits.</p>\n<p>The program requires the completion of three webinars and costs a total of $100 USD. To earn the certificate, you can attend the webinars live or view the recordings \u2013 or a combination of both.\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\" rel=\"noopener\" data-saferedirecturl=\"https://www.google.com/url?q=http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices/earn-a-certificate-in-social-media-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/&amp;source=gmail&amp;ust=1653256738392000&amp;usg=AOvVaw1o7aYZXpgFGzJb7CozPKzZ\">Learn more &amp; register</a>!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://www.nptechforgood.com/earn-a-certificate-in-digital-marketing-fundraising-from-nonprofit-tech-for-good/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone wp-image-37647 size-full\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=960%2C755&#038;ssl=1\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"755\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?w=1000&amp;ssl=1 1000w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=300%2C236&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=768%2C604&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/2024-Certificate-in-Digital-Marketing-and-Fundraising-for-Nonprofits.png?resize=50%2C39&amp;ssl=1 50w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n",
